{"tid":53852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[廢老]【爭產案關鍵】靠一條成人尿片證私生女身份 75歲婦要求分2000萬遺產","createTime":"2016-12-25T04:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T07:26:19.000Z","uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3128ea9494793d1af759c3f1c52c35950ff761f","tid":53852,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161225/large/1482638274_12f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161225%2Flarge%2F1482638274_12f6.jpg&h=f9dacc12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西班牙塞維利亞一名75歲婆婆聲稱透過DNA測試，證明自己是當地一個大地主的私生女，關鍵證物竟然是姑母的成人尿片。<br />\n<br />\n75歲的弗朗西斯卡（Francisca）透過律師入稟法院，要求繼承爸爸地主M（Jose M）逾250萬英鎊（2,382萬港元）的遺產。律師指，雖然地主M的遺體已被火化，但DNA測試已證實兩人有父女關係。<br />\n律師指，弗朗西斯卡早前聘請私家偵探跟蹤地主M的姊妹，亦即其姑母，最後在姑母物業外的垃圾筒找到「決定性證據」－－姑母的成人尿片，並藉此進行DNA測試，證明弗朗西斯卡就是M的女兒。<br />\n地主M生前與一位來自貧窮家庭的吉卜賽女子相戀，但雙方家人都反對，於是他便偷偷與該女子幽會，一生未娶。弗朗西斯卡的律師指，此事在弗朗西斯卡居住的地方眾所周知。<br />\n地主M去世後，親人原本只剩下一名姊妹。報道指暫時未知該姊妹會否就案件提出反對，亦未知法院需時多久才有判決。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》 <img src=\"http://staticlayout.apple.nextmedia.com/web_images/layout/art_end.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstaticlayout.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fweb_images%2Flayout%2Fart_end.gif&h=10b8c7d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161225/56090316\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161225%2F56090316&d=twUbOMYiiCgRTB8zOJLOKHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=f9cab5a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161225%2F56090316&h=db98b4b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161225/56090316</a><br />\n<br />\n咁撚老都去爭家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb463c0351d24e37feb2656e75ed6b3ecd16ef22","tid":53852,"uid":36544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"諗起梅媽"},{"pid":"b03c838a2117f05ebcdecd20f107403d860b1e46","tid":53852,"uid":8632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T07:26:19.000Z","msg":"2000萬就可以做大地主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}